IDE：eclipse<br>資料庫：Oracle  </p>
<hr>
<p>問題：資料庫帳號被鎖<br>原因：當時Eclipse有context.xml跟hibernate.cfg.xml檔(不同人寫的)，裡面的帳號一樣但是密碼不一樣，造成資料庫帳號被鎖。</p>
<p><img src="https://i.imgbox.com/TziEx2RA.png" alt=""></p>
<p>帳號被鎖的解決辦法：<br>利用Run SQL Command Line以system身份解鎖  </p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"></div><div class="line">SQL*Plus: Release 11.2.0.2.0 Production on 星期一 11月 28 15:33:11 2016</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">Copyright (c) 1982, 2010, Oracle.  All rights reserved.</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">SQL&gt; connect system</div><div class="line">Enter password:</div><div class="line">Connected.</div><div class="line">SQL&gt; alter user AA104G2 account unlock;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">User altered.</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">SQL&gt; commit;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">Commit complete.</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">SQL&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://i.imgbox.com/VBQfopO7.png" alt="">  </p>
<p>再從Oracle SQL Developer進入一次  </p>
<p><img src="https://i.imgbox.com/Sj80hIM1.png" alt="">  </p>
<p><strong>在SQL Developer 則可以用系統連線到&quot;其他使用者&quot;更改密碼，但要先解鎖。</strong></p>
<h2 id="重新建立連線"><a href="#重新建立連線" class="headerlink" title="重新建立連線"></a>重新建立連線</h2><p>這是下下策<br>做這件事之前要確定資料內容是不重要的。  </p>
<hr>
]]></content>
